'''The length of the bridge, which a train 130 metres long and travelling at 45 km/hr can cross in 30 seconds, is'''

Train=130
speed=45*5/18
time=30
print("The length of Bridge to find")
print("The Bridge Length + Train Length = Total Distance")
Bridge_Length=speed*time-Train
print(f'The length of bridge = {Bridge_Length}')
